He is our Last Hope. She is just a red panda.

He's name is Llorar.

Health = 112.5 (3/4  WILSON)
Hunger = 150 (WILSON)
drain Hunger = (3/4 WILSON)
Sanity = 200 (WILSON)
Sanity night_drain_mult = 0.5 (1/2 WILSON)
Sanity neg_aura_mult  = 0
Sanity ghost_drain_mult = 0

*He is dead.
*He is a cat.

She's name is Ri.

Health = 100
Hunger = 100
Sanity = 100
movement speed, drain hunger and sanity, damage multiplier change accordingly to phase of day
her best time is dusk, her bad time is day

*She is nocturnal and crepuscular.
*She can sleep on day and she has night vision.
